modName: AGTweaks - No Stone Unturned - into misc
summary:
This mod will move the \"No stone unturned\" (Stones of Barenziah quest) into the misc sections.
There is no need for such a side quest to be seperated.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/4505/7tw.png[/img]
[size=6]No Stone Unturned - into misc[/size]
[size=5]Made By Request[/size][/center]
 
 
 
[size=6]Description[/size]
[size=4]This mod will move the \"No stone unturned\" (Stones of Barenziah quest) into the misc sections.
There is no need for such a side quest to be seperated.[/size]

 
 
 
[size=6]Requirements[/size]
[size=4]None.[/size]
 
 
 
[size=6]Compatibility[/size]
Basically with everything.
 
 
[size=6]Installtion + Unistalltion[/size]
[size=4]Use the nod manager and everything should be fine.[/size]
